content.rendered:
Directed by K. Madhu

Written by S.N. Swamy

Star Mammootty (Sethurama Iyer). Kaniha (Dr. Susan George). Soubin Shahir (Paul Meyjo). Anoop Menon (Unnithan). Dileesh Pothan (Chief Minister). Swasika Vijay (Merlin). Asha Sharath (Adv. Prathibha S.). Sudev Nair (Iqbal Hussain). Malavika Menon (Aparna). Jagathi Sreekumar (Vikram). Kottayam Ramesh (Anwar). Prathap Pothen (Dr. George Abraham). Santhosh Keezhattoor (Baburaj). Renji Panicker (Balagopal). Mukesh (Chacko). Saikumar (Sathyadas). Chandhunath G. Nair (Bhasuran (as Chandunath)). Alexander Prasanth (Sudhi Nair). G. Suresh Kumar (Abdul Samad). Ansiba (Anitha Varma). Jayakrishnan (Josemon). Ramesh Pisharody (Vinay Menon). Arjun Nandakumar (Anil Thomas). Azees Nedumangad (Boban). Idavela Babu (Mammen Varghese). Pradeep Joseph (Bhasuran’s Friend)

Language Malayalam

Producers Swargachitra Appachan. Ibrahim Hamdan

Production Swargachitra
